<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type'/>
</head>
<body>
<p>The following dataset has been successfully deposited in the Illinois Data Bank:</p>
<blockquote>
  <%= @dataset.plain_text_citation %>
</blockquote>
<p>Here is some information about the deposited dataset:</p>
<blockquote>
  <p>DataCite DOI: <%= @dataset.identifier %></p>

  <p>Release date: <%= @dataset.release_date %></p>

  <p>Depositor: <%= @dataset.depositor_name %></p>

  <p>Contact person: <%= @dataset.corresponding_creator_name %></p>

  <p>Deposit agreement link: <a href="<%= root_url %>/datasets/<%= @dataset.key %>/review_deposit_agreement"></a></p>
</blockquote>

<p>
  A curator may contact you with questions about this dataset. Please direct any questions you may have at this time or
  in the future to <a href="mailto:databank@library.illinois.edu">databank@library.illinois.edu</a>.
</p>

<%= render partial: "sigblock_html" %>

</body>
</html>